    "body": "We generally prefer Solidity to assembly but we can't commit to never using assembly so this is not a request we can currently address.\r\n\r\nAs you can see in the comments in the latest version we don't have an alternative to assembly in this case:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/4961a51cc736c7d4aa9bd2e11e4cbbaff73efee9/contracts/utils/cryptography/ECDSA.sol#L65-L66\r\n\r\nI would suggest requesting the solang team to support EVM assembly.",
